OL,3,CTaxes for second home owners are 'a
OL,4,Csticking plaster' - campaigners
OL,6,FITV News' Charlotte Gay spent the day
OL,7,Fhearing from campaigners in Cornwall.
OL,9,FPeople across Devon and Cornwall are
OL,10,Fcautiously welcoming news that tax
OL,11,Fbreaks for second home owners are
OL,12,Fbeing scrapped, but campaigners say
OL,13,Fit's just a sticking plaster.
OL,15,FThe furnished lettings regime gave
OL,16,Flandlords tax breaks when they let out
OL,17,Fholiday homes for short periods.
