OL,6,FHowever campaigners say that's led to
OL,7,Fa big rise in holiday homes and a
OL,8,Fshortage of long term rentals for
OL,9,Flocal people.
OL,11,FCath Hayes from the Cornwall group
OL,12,FFirst Not Second Homes said: "There
OL,13,Fwill be ultimately some people that go
OL,14,Ffrom short term letting because it's
OL,15,Fde-incentivising it.
OL,17,F"But in terms of driving actual
OL,18,Fproperty into long term letting, no,
OL,19,Fit's not enough. It's a sticking
OL,20,Fplaster on a bleeding artery.
