OL,6,F"We've got a really serious situation
OL,7,Fhere that we can't build our way out
OL,8,Fof. And there is no shortage of
OL,9,Fhousing in Cornwall. It's how that
OL,10,Fhousing is being used."
OL,12,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt told the House
OL,13,Fof Commons: "In recent months
OL,14,Ffollowing tenacious representation
OL,15,Ffrom the honourable members for St
OL,16,FAustell and Newquay, North Devon,
OL,17,FCities of London and Westminster,
OL,18,FTorbay and Truro and Falmouth. I have
OL,19,Fbeen looking closely at our furnished
OL,20,Fholiday lettings tax regime.
