OL,3,CTaxes for second home owners are 'a
OL,4,Csticking plaster' - campaigners
OL,6,F"I am concerned that this tax regime
OL,7,Fis creating a distortion, meaning
OL,8,Fthere are not enough properties
OL,9,Favailable for long term rental by
OL,10,Flocal people. So to make the tax
OL,11,Fsystem work better for local
OL,12,Fcommunities. I'm going to abolish the
OL,13,Ffurnished holiday lettings regime."
OL,15,FThe regime gave landlords certain tax
OL,16,Fbreaks when they let holiday homes out
OL,17,Ffor short periods.
